'''诺曼·麦克雷'''（{{lang-en|Norman Macrae}}，{{bd|1923年||2010年|6月11日}}）是一位英国[[经济学家|经济学家]]、记者、作家<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/node/16374404?story_id=16374404 |title=The unacknowledged giant |work=[[The_Economist|The Economist]] |accessdate=2010-06-18 |date=17 June 2010 |archive-date=2017-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015230630/http://www.economist.com/node/16374404?story_id=16374404 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，获得过[[大英帝國勳章|大英帝國勳章]]和[[旭日章|旭日章]]<ref name="macrae406">Macrae, Norman. (2000). [https://books.google.com/books?id=OO-_gSRhe-EC&pg=PA406&lpg=PA406&dq=Norman+Macrae+Order+of+the+Rising+Sun&source=bl&ots=ikzmjf3PGb&sig=YAvffgvsZMApvAje3_i27Cy-fGM&hl=en&ei=djMMS67-JIa6lAfqj5yRBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CBEQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=&f=false ''John von Neumann: the Scientific Genius who Pioneered the Modern Computer, Game Theory, Nuclear Deterrence, and Much More'', Random House (1992), reprinted by the American Mathematical Society (2008), p. 406.] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OO-_gSRhe-EC&pg=PA406&lpg=PA406&dq=Norman+Macrae+Order+of+the+Rising+Sun&source=bl&ots=ikzmjf3PGb&sig=YAvffgvsZMApvAje3_i27Cy-fGM&hl=en&ei=djMMS67-JIa6lAfqj5yRBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CBEQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=&f=false |date=20130529101617 }}</ref>，主要作品有《天才的拓荒者：[[冯·诺伊曼|冯·诺伊曼]]传》（''John Von Neumann: The Scientific Genius Who Pioneered the Modern Computer, Game Theory, Nuclear Deterrence, and Much More''）等。

